00:26:33.490 --> 00:26:35.860 align:middle line:84%
When I think of
that journey that

00:26:35.860 --> 00:26:40.930 align:middle line:84%
compels us to keep
searching, what

00:26:40.930 --> 00:26:43.090 align:middle line:90%
are we always searching for?

00:26:43.090 --> 00:26:48.820 align:middle line:84%
We're searching for the
capacity to liberate ourselves

00:26:48.820 --> 00:26:53.530 align:middle line:84%
to be able to make
these choices in life

00:26:53.530 --> 00:26:57.640 align:middle line:90%
that are the most outrageous--

00:26:57.640 --> 00:27:00.910 align:middle line:84%
not outrageous by
financial means,

00:27:00.910 --> 00:27:04.420 align:middle line:84%
but outrageously
empowering of self

00:27:04.420 --> 00:27:07.360 align:middle line:90%
and others at the same time.

00:27:07.360 --> 00:27:12.700 align:middle line:84%
Because that truly, is the
ultimate spiritual path.

00:27:12.700 --> 00:27:14.520 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

